{"type": "article", "id": 25311, "title": "极简水池", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-12T06:35:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 83, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702153211vWzsiUnxbfVZ9L68.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一组遵循“少即是多”原理的洗手池设计，水池是圆形或方形的，深度较浅。方形水池边缘保留了直角转折，在内侧经过了些微的倾斜处理，而圆形或椭圆形水池则凸显出水池的流动性，极具几何感。水龙头分为在水池外或水池中两种，很高，形状也与较规整的几何水池形成对比，突出了水池本身的极简和干净。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153206HDrhmovQCON3XtnL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153207g0yWVomu1h9lLPKi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83055556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153209mXI29ljrzi1xtWAq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153210nSctwxgHpsik5Fuo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153210yr41JujemwHWPgMl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64305556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}